1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 50-06.1 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to minimum wage paid by the department of health and human services
3 under the senior community service employment program.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
5 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 50-06.1 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
6 and enacted as follows:
7 Senior community service employment program - Minimum wage.
8 The minimum hourly wage for individuals paid by the department under the senior
9 community service employment program is twelve dollars or the amount established by the
10 department by administrative rule, within the limits of legislative appropriation.
